Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我还真的是吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩就突然对花菱学长吻了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷跟我一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.43,0:01:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.64,0:01:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 这到底是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十二话  接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 花菱少爷 随你喜欢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 我过去啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 等一下 稍微等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.63,0:02:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了 请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.90,0:02:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那个不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.21,0:02:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷抽到鬼牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 轮到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要抽哪个才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.49,0:02:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？还要玩啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 这个房间布偶真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.97,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸因为我从小就很喜欢布偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.51,0:02:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就买了一堆给我当礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是8岁的生日礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左边的是11岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那边的是14岁的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都是我爸爸送我的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.35,0:03:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明都已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.96,0:03:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该睡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.33,0:03:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 我该去哪个房间睡好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟花菱少爷一起睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你拜托你嘛 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您还没有去睡吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我现在就去睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到小繭你睡着为止喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么关灯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.85,0:04:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又任性 害的花菱少爷困扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没这回事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.19,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我是坏孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我做了坏事的话请骂我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭并不是坏孩子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安 小兔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭 还是这么珍惜它啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你一直想要的兔子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了呢 小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然早了一个礼拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这是繭12岁的生日礼物喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 我的生日宴会呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起啊 繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.97,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸跟妈妈明天开始都必须到外国去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次只要两个月就会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后大家再一起开宴会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样就不叫生日宴会了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这都是为了工作喔 小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你谅解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美幸社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 稀客稀客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是盛大的宴会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是美幸纺织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不不不 这都是靠大家的帮忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要喝点什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.52,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 太太 请不要那么客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸 那个前几天我在学校…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.83,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起啊 繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些话我之后再好好听你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 社长 请来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 就是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国语的考试我拿了100分喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 我先离开一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈现在有重要的事情要谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先喝这个等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是学校的理事长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.89,0:07:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来打个招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭 你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快打个招呼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是非常抱歉 我们家的女儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到会这个样子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个 是你的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 是你掉的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是说了我不知道吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是爸爸自作主张买来给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不知道这种东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊勒？没回答啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.93,0:08:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？那么没精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你在这种地方做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.58,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 还没自我介绍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面 我的名字叫小兔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.71,0:08:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兔子的小兔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多指教喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇怪的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 那你的名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美幸…繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭啊 好名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.03,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我啊 我是想跟你一起玩才过来的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小繭你爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我一堆同伴中努力的挑中我的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭的爸爸是很好的人对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他挑中我了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最讨厌爸爸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.69,0:09:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半年才见他一面 他却都不和我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不来我的生日宴会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朋友的生日宴会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的爸爸妈妈都会为他们庆祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢琴发表会时 也会来称赞他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我没人称赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为爸爸妈妈都不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不重视我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好啊 小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你还有爸爸妈妈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔的爸爸跟妈妈呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是去外国了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.27,0:10:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美国？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加拿大？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 更远的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是法国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 英国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了更远、更远的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？更远的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.69,0:10:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也见不到爸爸跟妈妈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.59,0:10:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我都是孤单一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个人是很寂寞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很难过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很悲哀的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我认为小繭的爸爸跟妈妈都很重视你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.44,0:10:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比世界上任何一个人都爱小繭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以小繭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要讨厌你爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吗？小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了 小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还会再来玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会再见面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我会再来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会等你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫薰 花菱薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真伤脑筋 这样就离不开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？一副要死的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜学姐是严重的宿醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.85,0:12:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡眠不足的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡眠不足？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.29,0:12:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱学长昨晚在那女孩子家住对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.23,0:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长真是深藏不露啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.83,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你昨晚要跟那女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的头…要死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.71,0:12:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是今天小繭没来真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来的话一定又是一场大骚动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟花菱少爷一起去大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭大小姐的课程下个礼拜才开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚果然发生了什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？花菱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.77,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 要打个电话给小葵才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于那个预算等跟你见面再谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 请稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.77,0:13:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 札幌那边能够很快的修理的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从刚才就一直在讲话中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是笑嘻嘻的料理时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来 今天准备了相当新鲜的素材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算为您介绍鱼料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备好的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.66,0:13:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正值美味时期的鮸鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接吻？而且正是时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然对花菱学长吻了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.11,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我要住在朋友的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.61,0:14:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么样的人啊？那个朋友…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚也跟那个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 我在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行 这种时候才更要振作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 先来洗衣服来转换心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.13,0:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长初吻是什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么突然问这个问题？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是几岁的时候啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说那个时候的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个不是接吻 只是纯粹的打招呼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭也说过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.75,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是普通的女孩子不会那样想喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我的恋人被人用接吻来打招呼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会坐立不安的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接吻…的确…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是不可抗力 接吻毕竟是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是去道个歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是小葵又不知道这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以还是不要说奇怪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 我去换个衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.39,0:15:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 还是说一下比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回来了啊 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚餐马上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 有事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 不 其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件必须要说的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须要说的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是关于…昨天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.65,0:15:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 你又喝酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还在准备晚餐中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有话之后再慢慢说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰也来喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呜…我还想喝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这样喝就已经够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等她整理完就说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.96,0:16:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来接吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以跟那个女孩接吻 我就不行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.11,0:16:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接一两次吻又不会少一块肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接吻啦 你明明都吻过那个女孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就说那不是吻她 而是被她吻啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭也说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是打招呼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.89,0:17:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…来打招呼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不吻我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就去吻房东 去吻管理员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问什么会变成那样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吻小妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到那个笑脸 心就有点痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会不会变成不可挽回的事态啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.99,0:17:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好过份 都已经有我了 还跟其他的人接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还住在那个女孩子的家 还做出这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个婚约就此取消吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你接下来要说的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.68,0:18:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的事…你刚刚回来的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.79,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.66,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的朋友是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像妹妹一样的…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的确是接过吻没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 那个女孩是归国子女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接吻是打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候会住在她家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为她孤单一个人 很寂寞的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是并没有做什么奇怪的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 也许接吻算是很奇怪的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我的恋人被人用接吻来打招呼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会坐立不安的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 总之对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你 请不要跟我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你那样道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.71,0:19:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道为什么会有种难过的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为薰的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.66,0:19:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比任何人都要了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论发生什么事 我都相信薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要跟我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.95,0:19:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 下次的摄影展请带我去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有点不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.93,0:20:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以再答应我一件任性的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 可以 什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…所以说…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 没关系的 没什么事情啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都说到这样反而更在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说吧 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.82,0:20:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么都会听的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.69,0:20:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请跟我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.66,0:20:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请跟我…接吻…
